		{"id":"c3d5ae1cc2d8e79f","type":"text","text":"```dataview  \nTASK  \nWHERE (contains(tags, \"#calendar\") OR contains(tags, \"#holiday\"))  \nAND scheduled = date(today)  \nGROUP by scheduled  \n```\n---\n```dataview  \nTASK  \nWHERE (contains(tags, \"#calendar\") OR contains(tags, \"#holiday\"))  \nAND (scheduled >= date(tomorrow) AND scheduled <= date(today) + dur(7 days))  \nSORT scheduled ASC  \nGROUP by scheduled  \n```","x":-660,"y":-60,"width":560,"height":440},
